Detailed Description

A class to manage track reconstruction in AMS Tracker.

AMSTrTrack is a core of track reconstruction routines. The algorithm is imported from AMSTrTrack but mostly rewritten with following modifications: (1) Made simpler and easier to read (2) Completely independent of Gbatch (stand alone) (3) Generating the same results but faster (by ~50%)

Date:
2007/12/03 SH First import (just a copy of trrec.C in Gbatch)

2007/12/20 SH TkFit support

2007/12/28 SH First stable vertion after a refinement

2008/01/21 SH Imported to tkdev (test version)

2008/02/13 SH Comments are updated

2008/03/01 AO Preliminary new data format

2008/03/12 SH Getting back to SH version

Date
2008/11/06 19:29:51
